  "title": "Senior Data Engineer (Azure/ MNC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead the design, development, and day-to-day operation of the enterprise cloud data platform onAzure.</li><li>Build and maintain scalable data pipelines using Azure Databricks and PySpark.</li><li>Design and manage data ingestion and orchestration workflows using Azure Data Factory.</li><li>Implement and manage data governance, access control, and metadata using Unity Catalog.</li><li>Develop and maintain Lakehouse data models (Bronze, Silver, Gold layers).</li><li>Optimize platform performance, reliability, and cloud costs across Databricks workloads.</li><li>Troubleshoot data pipeline issues and drive continuous platform improvements.</li><li>Provide technical guidance and best practices to data engineers and stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in IT, Computer Science or related technical field.</li><li>Strong hands-on experience with <strong>Azure Databricks</strong> and <strong>PySpark</strong> in production environments.</li><li>Experience building and orchestrating data pipelines using <strong>Azure Data Factory</strong>.</li><li>Solid understanding of data governance, security, and access management, including <strong>Unity Catalog</strong>.</li><li>Proven experience designing and supporting scalable cloud data platforms on <strong>Microsoft Azure</strong>.</li></ul><p><br />Please submit your updated resume in Word format by using the <strong>Apply Now Button.</strong><br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />Email resume to <strong>ken.ng@peopleprofilers.com</strong><br />People Profilers Pte Ltd, 20 Cecil Street,#08-09, PLUS Building, Singapore 049705.<br />Tel: 6950 9724<br /><a href=\"http://www.peopleprofilers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.peopleprofilers.com<br /></a>EA License Number: 02C4944<br />Registration Number: R1872398<br />Posting Personnel: Ng Jwee Ken<br />Ref: 3WWYY79W</p>",
